## 🔤 Font Pairings

### Headings
- Playfair Display (Serif) — elegant, trustworthy
- Fallback: Georgia, serif

### Body Text
- Open Sans — clean, friendly, highly readable
- Fallback: Arial, sans-serif

### Multilingual Support
- Noto Sans — excellent for Amharic, Oromo, Tigrinya
- Fallback: Helvetica, sans-serif

